Definition: large tree of Trinidad and Guyana having odd-pinnate leaves and violet-scented axillary racemes of yellow flowers and long smooth pods
Example: grown as a specimen in parks and large gardens
Synonyms: Platymiscium_trinitatis, quira, large, tree, of, Trinidad, and, Guyana, having, odd-pinnate, leaves, violet-scented, axillary, racemes, yellow, flowers, long, smooth, pods, grown, as, a, specimen, in, parks, gardens
Category: noun.plant
